page.title: 14A WEDNESDAY IN DARLINGTON
page.content: At 7.15 in the morning my dad wakes me. After breakfast,if I have time I do my piano practice. With my bag on my shoulder I set off to school.When I get there we have assembly,and then P.E. After play its maths,I hope it isn't mental.Suddenly the bell goes for dinner.I finish the sum that I'm doing and go home for dinner.I generally have a snack with a main meal at tea time. After lunch it's French. I enjoy that. We have recorder later,when we play lots of different pieces. After school, I go straight to the Arts Centre for a piano lesson,which I share with my sister.I have tea at home and then go to Guides.Thats my favourite part of the day.I don't get to bed until about 10.00p.m. because that is when I get home from Guides.
